snippet.title: Basic Guide to Catopia Rush - Cat-Action RPG on Android and iOS 2021
snippet.description:
Community Manager Alex breaks down the basics of Catopia: Rush, the latest game from Supercolony on Android and iOS. Get a tour of the kingdom, explore the various available systems, and learn some quick tips. 

Catopia: Rush is available now via a soft launch in over 150 regions with more regions and improvements being added for a global launch on June 2nd. 

*Game details are subject to change between now and full release*

Download or wishlist in the links below:
Google Play - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.supercolony.catopia
Apple App Store - https://apps.apple.com/app/catopia-rush/id1481412678

Don't forget to leave us feedback and follow our socials!
https://www.supercolony.com/
